  "content": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n  <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n  <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n  <title>Terminal Share</title>\n  <style>\n    :root {\n      --bg-color: #1e1e1e;\n      --text-color: #f8f8f8;\n      --header-bg: #333;\n      --border-color: #555;\n      --accent-color: #88c0d0;\n    }\n    \n    body {\n      font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;\n      margin: 0;\n      padding: 0;\n      background-color: var(--bg-color);\n      color: var(--text-color);\n      line-height: 1.6;\n    }\n    \n    .container {\n      max-width: 800px;\n      margin: 0 auto;\n      padding: 40px 20px;\n    }\n    \n    h1 {\n      color: var(--accent-color);\n      margin-bottom: 30px;\n    }\n    \n    .card {\n      background-color: var(--header-bg);\n      border-radius: 8px;\n      padding: 25px;\n      margin-bottom: 30px;\n      border: 1px solid var(--border-color);\n    }\n    \n    pre {\n      background-color: #222;\n      padding: 15px;\n      border-radius: 5px;\n      overflow-x: auto;\n      font-family: 'Fira Code', monospace;\n    }\n    \n    code {\n      font-family: 'Fira Code', monospace;\n    }\n    \n    .highlight {\n      color: #a3be8c;\n    }\n    \n    .command {\n      color: #ebcb8b;\n    }\n    \n    a {\n      color: var(--accent-color);\n      text-decoration: none;\n    }\n    \n    a:hover {\n      text-decoration: underline;\n    }\n    \n    .footer {\n      margin-top: 50px;\n      text-align: center;\n      font-size: 14px;\n      color: #888;\n    }\n  </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n  <div class=\"container\">\n    <h1>Terminal Share</h1>\n    \n    <div class=\"card\">\n      <h2>Share Terminal Output with Style</h2>\n      <p>\n        Terminal Share lets you easily share command output with syntax highlighting and themes.\n        Just run a command with <code>tshare</code> and get a sharable link instantly.\n      </p>\n      \n      <h3>Installation</h3>\n      <p>Download the client script and make it executable:</p>\n      <pre><code>curl -o /usr/local/bin/tshare https://example.com/tshare\nchmod +x /usr/local/bin/tshare</code></pre>\n      \n      <h3>Usage</h3>\n      <p>Use it just like <code>time</code>:</p>\n      <pre><code><span class=\"command\">tshare ls -la</span>\n<span class=\"command\">tshare -s python script.py</span></code></pre>\n    </div>\n    \n    <div class=\"card\">\n      <h3>Features</h3>\n      <ul>\n        <li><span class=\"highlight\">Beautiful syntax highlighting</span> with multiple themes</li>\n        <li><span class=\"highlight\">Context information</span> showing the hostname, directory, and command</li>\n        <li><span class=\"highlight\">Simple usage</span> - just prepend any command with <code>tshare</code></li>\n        <li><span class=\"highlight\">Automatic clipboard copy</span> of sharable URLs</li>\n      </ul>\n    </div>\n    \n    <div class=\"footer\">\n      Terminal Share - A better way to share terminal output\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</body>\n</html>",
